para_sentences.para_0: This quiz will test your understanding of the material covered so far this week (MLOs).
para_sentences.para_1: This is an online quiz. There will be no time limit to the quiz. You can attempt the quiz twice and the best of the scores will be retained. This is open notes and open internet quiz but refrain from discussing with anybody during the exam.
para_sentences.para_2: Note that this test cannot be taken past the due date for any credit.
para_sentences.para_4: You can view the correct answers here after the due date.
